  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]<strong> </span>cold water</strong> to a small bowl with your <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>dried oregano </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and mix to combine – this is your <strong>tomato sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
